data.description: Beachy 5 bedroom 3 full bath custom built home with heated in ground gunite salt water swimming pool! Detached workshop/mother in law suite. Home currently has ADT security and fiber optics, natural gas supplied within the community. Only minutes from charter and public schools. Huge selection of nearby restaurants and shopping  as well as Lynn Haven Beach with boat ramps. 12.8 miles from Panama City's best beaches!  Tyndall Air Force base is only 14 miles away. This beachy custom built home includes many architectural details such as beautiful ceramic tile and carpet throughout with a floor plan that will blow you away. Two car garage and a fully decked floor in the attic with plenty of storage along with plenty of storage within the home. A large 18' X 14' detached workshop/mother in law plan that is heated and cooled. Enjoy your private, heated salt water 28' X 14' in ground swimming pool with automatic controls and pool cleaner make it nearly hands free. Entering the home you will notice a double tray ceiling highlighted by crown molding as well as a mantle and electric fireplace. The formal dining room also has double tray ceiling. The kitchen is the heart of the home with G E Cafe refrigerator. Double oven and over counter microwave/convection. But wait! The master is the must see with vaulted ceiling, his and her walk in closets with pocket doors. Oversized jetted tub, walk in shower with glass door. You will not be disappointed! In July of 2023 a new water heater, garage door opener and swimming pool pump were installed. Nicely landscaped with large tree and automatic sprinkler/irrigation system. Pictures cannot show enough of the beauty of this well located home. Home can be purchased fully furnished so all you have to do is buy it and move in!
